00:12:06.030 --> 00:12:09.600 align:middle line:10%
In June 1852,
"Scientific American"

00:12:09.600 --> 00:12:12.390 align:middle line:10%
carried an article about
an exquisitely fashioned

00:12:12.390 --> 00:12:15.360 align:middle line:10%
metallic vase blasted
from a solid rock

00:12:15.360 --> 00:12:17.130 align:middle line:10%
in Dorchester, Massachusetts.

00:12:17.130 --> 00:12:20.060 align:middle line:10%


00:12:20.060 --> 00:12:23.210 align:middle line:10%
The US Geological Survey
reports that this rock

00:12:23.210 --> 00:12:27.150 align:middle line:10%
is pre-Cambrian in age,
over 600 million years old.

00:12:27.150 --> 00:12:29.920 align:middle line:10%


00:12:29.920 --> 00:12:33.130 align:middle line:10%
Such discoveries
continue to be made.

00:12:33.130 --> 00:12:36.670 align:middle line:10%
In 1968, several
metallic tubes were

00:12:36.670 --> 00:12:40.540 align:middle line:10%
found in a Cretaceous chalk
bed in northern France.

00:12:40.540 --> 00:12:43.390 align:middle line:10%
The discoverers,
[INAUDIBLE] and [INAUDIBLE],,

00:12:43.390 --> 00:12:45.510 align:middle line:10%
thought them to be the
product of human work.

00:12:45.510 --> 00:12:48.390 align:middle line:90%


00:12:48.390 --> 00:12:51.640 align:middle line:84%
The Cretaceous lies
between the Mesozoic period

00:12:51.640 --> 00:12:55.720 align:middle line:84%
and dates from 65 to
140 million years ago.

00:12:55.720 --> 00:12:59.500 align:middle line:90%


00:12:59.500 --> 00:13:01.810 align:middle line:84%
This evidence so
radically violates

00:13:01.810 --> 00:13:04.420 align:middle line:84%
current scientific
conceptions that it's

00:13:04.420 --> 00:13:07.180 align:middle line:84%
hard to make sense
out of it at all.

00:13:07.180 --> 00:13:10.150 align:middle line:84%
But we may gain greater
insight by considering

00:13:10.150 --> 00:13:13.180 align:middle line:84%
another area in which
human nature violates

00:13:13.180 --> 00:13:19.150 align:middle line:84%
standard scientific views,
the domain of the paranormal.

00:13:19.150 --> 00:13:23.050 align:middle line:84%
Although most scientists
reject paranormal phenomena,

00:13:23.050 --> 00:13:25.870 align:middle line:84%
others have carefully
investigated them.

00:13:25.870 --> 00:13:29.860 align:middle line:84%
One was Sir William Crookes,
the famous British physicist

00:13:29.860 --> 00:13:32.320 align:middle line:84%
who invented the cathode
ray tube now used

00:13:32.320 --> 00:13:33.830 align:middle line:90%
in television screens.

00:13:33.830 --> 00:13:37.810 align:middle line:84%
Crookes became president of
the prestigious Royal Society

00:13:37.810 --> 00:13:40.210 align:middle line:84%
and eventually
received a Nobel Prize

00:13:40.210 --> 00:13:42.520 align:middle line:90%
for his discovery of thallium.

00:13:42.520 --> 00:13:45.070 align:middle line:84%
Crookes began his
investigations in order

00:13:45.070 --> 00:13:48.160 align:middle line:84%
to expose fraudulent
psychics, but then

00:13:48.160 --> 00:13:51.820 align:middle line:84%
became convinced of the
reality of psychic phenomena.

00:13:51.820 --> 00:13:55.420 align:middle line:84%
One of the psychics he tested
was Daniel Dunglas Home,

00:13:55.420 --> 00:13:59.590 align:middle line:84%
a medium famous among European
aristocrats and literati

00:13:59.590 --> 00:14:02.830 align:middle line:84%
for the remarkable unexplained
physical effects that occurred

00:14:02.830 --> 00:14:05.650 align:middle line:90%
regularly in his presence.

00:14:05.650 --> 00:14:08.380 align:middle line:10%
With this apparatus,
Crookes demonstrated

00:14:08.380 --> 00:14:11.080 align:middle line:10%
that Home could, by
touching his fingers lightly

00:14:11.080 --> 00:14:14.500 align:middle line:10%
on a match box positioned
here, cause the scale

00:14:14.500 --> 00:14:16.510 align:middle line:10%
at the other end of
the board to register

00:14:16.510 --> 00:14:19.720 align:middle line:10%
six pounds of pressure.

00:14:19.720 --> 00:14:23.140 align:middle line:84%
With a mechanical
disadvantage of about 20,

00:14:23.140 --> 00:14:26.860 align:middle line:84%
Home would have had to exert
some 120 pounds of pressure

00:14:26.860 --> 00:14:30.010 align:middle line:84%
to do this, according
to standard physics.

00:14:30.010 --> 00:14:33.400 align:middle line:84%
And more extraordinary
experiments were to follow.

00:14:33.400 --> 00:14:37.480 align:middle line:84%
People had often observed an
accordion play complex tunes

00:14:37.480 --> 00:14:41.830 align:middle line:84%
while Home held it with only one
hand, away from the keyboard.

00:14:41.830 --> 00:14:44.890 align:middle line:84%
To ensure that Home was
not in fact manipulating

00:14:44.890 --> 00:14:47.570 align:middle line:84%
the instrument by
sleight of hand,

00:14:47.570 --> 00:14:50.270 align:middle line:84%
Crookes constructed
a special cage.

00:14:50.270 --> 00:14:52.600 align:middle line:84%
When positioned
beneath the table,

00:14:52.600 --> 00:14:54.970 align:middle line:84%
the cage made it
impossible for Home

00:14:54.970 --> 00:14:58.420 align:middle line:84%
to touch the instrument
with his other hand.

00:14:58.420 --> 00:15:02.330 align:middle line:84%
As a safeguard against a trick
mechanism in the accordion,

00:15:02.330 --> 00:15:06.740 align:middle line:84%
Crookes supplied a brand new
accordion never seen by Homes.

00:15:06.740 --> 00:15:10.910 align:middle line:84%
Crookes reported that the
accordion played as usual.

00:15:10.910 --> 00:15:13.942 align:middle line:84%
Then Home removed his
hand from the cage.

00:15:13.942 --> 00:15:17.300 align:middle line:84%
Crookes states, "I and
two of the others present

00:15:17.300 --> 00:15:21.260 align:middle line:84%
saw the accordion distinctly
floating about inside the cage

00:15:21.260 --> 00:15:23.830 align:middle line:90%
with no visible support."

00:15:23.830 --> 00:15:28.420 align:middle line:84%
Wallace reported a
similar experience.

00:15:28.420 --> 00:15:31.390 align:middle line:84%
On several occasions,
observers--

00:15:31.390 --> 00:15:35.030 align:middle line:84%
including Crookes--
saw Home levitate.

00:15:35.030 --> 00:15:38.530 align:middle line:84%
When Home levitated, he
claimed he was not doing it

00:15:38.530 --> 00:15:42.520 align:middle line:84%
by his own power, but was being
lifted by invisible sentient

00:15:42.520 --> 00:15:43.720 align:middle line:90%
beings.

00:15:43.720 --> 00:15:46.090 align:middle line:84%
Levitation by
professional magicians

00:15:46.090 --> 00:15:50.620 align:middle line:84%
requires an elaborate apparatus
concealed upon a stage,

00:15:50.620 --> 00:15:53.530 align:middle line:84%
whereas the levitations
by Home took place

00:15:53.530 --> 00:15:57.040 align:middle line:84%
in the midst of crowds of
guests in private residences

00:15:57.040 --> 00:16:00.100 align:middle line:90%
where he was a dinner guest.

00:16:00.100 --> 00:16:03.070 align:middle line:84%
We find well-attested
reports of levitation

00:16:03.070 --> 00:16:05.710 align:middle line:84%
from a variety of
times and places.

00:16:05.710 --> 00:16:10.650 align:middle line:84%
For example, in 17th century
Italy, St. Joseph of Cupertino

00:16:10.650 --> 00:16:14.320 align:middle line:84%
often floated into the
air, a phenomenon witnessed

00:16:14.320 --> 00:16:19.000 align:middle line:84%
by Pope Urban VIII, the Spanish
ambassador to the papal court,

00:16:19.000 --> 00:16:21.910 align:middle line:84%
and the Duke of
Brunswick, a Lutheran.

00:16:21.910 --> 00:16:24.280 align:middle line:84%
"About these phenomena,"
Professor Challis

00:16:24.280 --> 00:16:27.280 align:middle line:84%
of Cambridge University
said, "the testimony

00:16:27.280 --> 00:16:30.400 align:middle line:84%
has been so abundant that either
the facts must be admitted

00:16:30.400 --> 00:16:33.610 align:middle line:84%
to be such as they are
reported or the possibility

00:16:33.610 --> 00:16:38.500 align:middle line:84%
of certifying facts by human
testimony must be given up."

00:16:38.500 --> 00:16:41.230 align:middle line:10%
Anomalous facts connected
with the paranormal

00:16:41.230 --> 00:16:43.420 align:middle line:10%
and the high
antiquity of man tend

00:16:43.420 --> 00:16:47.110 align:middle line:10%
to be rejected by the
scientific community.

00:16:47.110 --> 00:16:50.200 align:middle line:10%
This reveals the working
of a knowledge filter

00:16:50.200 --> 00:16:52.240 align:middle line:10%
by which people
preserve information

00:16:52.240 --> 00:16:56.140 align:middle line:10%
compatible with their views
and eliminate information

00:16:56.140 --> 00:16:58.900 align:middle line:10%
at odds with their views.

00:16:58.900 --> 00:17:02.800 align:middle line:10%
Science has carefully filtered
out all information connected

00:17:02.800 --> 00:17:04.660 align:middle line:10%
with the paranormal.

00:17:04.660 --> 00:17:08.020 align:middle line:84%
But if we survey human
society in general,

00:17:08.020 --> 00:17:11.710 align:middle line:84%
we find abundant evidence that
such phenomena have occurred

00:17:11.710 --> 00:17:13.630 align:middle line:90%
in almost all times and places.

00:17:13.630 --> 00:17:17.220 align:middle line:90%


00:17:17.220 --> 00:17:20.609 align:middle line:90%
Very widespread is shamanism.

00:17:20.609 --> 00:17:24.030 align:middle line:84%
In trance, shamans
contact spirits,

00:17:24.030 --> 00:17:26.520 align:middle line:84%
enabling them to
produce varieties

00:17:26.520 --> 00:17:32.020 align:middle line:84%
of paranormal phenomena,
including psychic healing.

00:17:32.020 --> 00:17:34.540 align:middle line:84%
A fundamental
element of shamanism

00:17:34.540 --> 00:17:37.830 align:middle line:84%
and of many other traditions
ancient and modern

00:17:37.830 --> 00:17:41.290 align:middle line:84%
is there is a soul that is
distinct from the physical body

00:17:41.290 --> 00:17:44.050 align:middle line:84%
and which can travel
outside of it.

00:17:44.050 --> 00:17:47.770 align:middle line:84%
Some evidence for this comes
from modern medical science.

00:17:47.770 --> 00:17:52.360 align:middle line:84%
Physicians encounter reports
of out-of-body experiences.

00:17:52.360 --> 00:17:55.060 align:middle line:84%
These typically occur
during heart attacks

00:17:55.060 --> 00:17:58.120 align:middle line:90%
and other traumatic experiences.

00:17:58.120 --> 00:18:00.850 align:middle line:84%
Many people reported
observing their own body

00:18:00.850 --> 00:18:03.160 align:middle line:90%
from a vantage point above it.

00:18:03.160 --> 00:18:07.930 align:middle line:84%
Dr. Michael Sabom, initially
skeptical of such experiences,

00:18:07.930 --> 00:18:10.510 align:middle line:90%
sought to confirm them.

00:18:10.510 --> 00:18:12.580 align:middle line:84%
He requested heart
attack patients

00:18:12.580 --> 00:18:15.280 align:middle line:84%
reporting out-of-body
experiences

00:18:15.280 --> 00:18:18.280 align:middle line:84%
to give details of their
exact medical treatment

00:18:18.280 --> 00:18:21.320 align:middle line:84%
during the time they
were unconscious.

00:18:21.320 --> 00:18:24.280 align:middle line:84%
In the group that he studied,
enough people correctly

00:18:24.280 --> 00:18:26.500 align:middle line:84%
related details
of their treatment

00:18:26.500 --> 00:18:29.860 align:middle line:84%
to convince Sabom that the
out-of-body experiences had

00:18:29.860 --> 00:18:31.490 align:middle line:90%
indeed occurred.

00:18:31.490 --> 00:18:34.450 align:middle line:84%
Sabom questioned,
and we quote, "Could

00:18:34.450 --> 00:18:37.330 align:middle line:84%
the mind, which splits apart
from the physical brain,

00:18:37.330 --> 00:18:40.060 align:middle line:84%
be in essence the
soul which continues

00:18:40.060 --> 00:18:42.730 align:middle line:84%
to exist after the
final bodily death,

00:18:42.730 --> 00:18:45.430 align:middle line:84%
according to some
religious doctrines?

00:18:45.430 --> 00:18:48.580 align:middle line:84%
As I see it, this is
the ultimate question

00:18:48.580 --> 00:18:51.610 align:middle line:84%
that has been raised by reports
of near-death experiences."

00:18:51.610 --> 00:18:55.210 align:middle line:90%


00:18:55.210 --> 00:18:59.530 align:middle line:84%
This leads us to the question of
transmigration, the transferral

00:18:59.530 --> 00:19:02.800 align:middle line:84%
of a conscious entity from
one physical body to another

00:19:02.800 --> 00:19:05.080 align:middle line:90%
at the time of death.

00:19:05.080 --> 00:19:08.200 align:middle line:84%
Dr. Ian Stevenson,
a psychiatrist

00:19:08.200 --> 00:19:11.020 align:middle line:84%
at the University of
Virginia, has extensively

00:19:11.020 --> 00:19:13.750 align:middle line:84%
compiled reports
indicating people

00:19:13.750 --> 00:19:17.610 align:middle line:84%
are able to remember
previous lives.

00:19:17.610 --> 00:19:20.490 align:middle line:84%
Stevenson studied reports
by very young children

00:19:20.490 --> 00:19:24.300 align:middle line:84%
not under hypnosis with neither
the motive nor the ability

00:19:24.300 --> 00:19:27.480 align:middle line:84%
to invent elaborate
past life stories.

00:19:27.480 --> 00:19:29.760 align:middle line:84%
The reports of the
previous incarnation

00:19:29.760 --> 00:19:33.800 align:middle line:84%
often included details of the
person's habits, belongings,

00:19:33.800 --> 00:19:35.670 align:middle line:90%
and acquaintances.

00:19:35.670 --> 00:19:39.420 align:middle line:10%
In many cases, Stevenson was
able to verify the details

00:19:39.420 --> 00:19:42.300 align:middle line:10%
and confirm that the
previous personality did,

00:19:42.300 --> 00:19:44.310 align:middle line:10%
in fact, exist.

00:19:44.310 --> 00:19:49.530 align:middle line:10%
As of 1988, Stevenson
had tabulated 2,500 cases

00:19:49.530 --> 00:19:51.530 align:middle line:10%
from around the world.

00:19:51.530 --> 00:19:55.350 align:middle line:10%
881 of these were
thoroughly investigated

00:19:55.350 --> 00:19:58.110 align:middle line:10%
and Stevenson was able
to verify the reported

00:19:58.110 --> 00:20:04.380 align:middle line:10%
previous incarnation in
546 instances, about 62%

00:20:04.380 --> 00:20:07.950 align:middle line:10%
of the total cases investigated.

00:20:07.950 --> 00:20:11.640 align:middle line:84%
Such extensive evidence suggests
that the human personality

00:20:11.640 --> 00:20:14.520 align:middle line:84%
can function outside
the physical body

00:20:14.520 --> 00:20:18.120 align:middle line:84%
and even transmigrate
from one body to another.

00:20:18.120 --> 00:20:21.450 align:middle line:84%
This indicates that some
elements of human existence

00:20:21.450 --> 00:20:24.240 align:middle line:84%
are incompatible
with physical science

00:20:24.240 --> 00:20:26.700 align:middle line:90%
and its evolutionary theories.

00:20:26.700 --> 00:20:32.040 align:middle line:84%
Such elements leave no
record in the Earth's strata.

00:20:32.040 --> 00:20:35.640 align:middle line:84%
Some insist, however, that
all paranormal phenomena

00:20:35.640 --> 00:20:38.760 align:middle line:84%
have been the result of
illusion and cheating.

00:20:38.760 --> 00:20:43.710 align:middle line:84%
Nonetheless, spirits,
levitation, miraculous healing,

00:20:43.710 --> 00:20:47.100 align:middle line:84%
out-of-body experiences,
and transmigration

00:20:47.100 --> 00:20:50.400 align:middle line:84%
have been consistently
observed in human societies

00:20:50.400 --> 00:20:53.920 align:middle line:84%
all over the world for
thousands of years.

00:20:53.920 --> 00:20:56.730 align:middle line:84%
Critics argue that the
human mind everywhere

00:20:56.730 --> 00:20:58.740 align:middle line:90%
generates similar delusions.

00:20:58.740 --> 00:21:01.990 align:middle line:84%
But if the human mind
is everywhere the same,

00:21:01.990 --> 00:21:05.340 align:middle line:84%
the power to discriminate
between reality and illusion

00:21:05.340 --> 00:21:07.590 align:middle line:90%
should also be widespread.

00:21:07.590 --> 00:21:10.380 align:middle line:10%
Must we assume that the
most intelligent people

00:21:10.380 --> 00:21:14.840 align:middle line:10%
in nearly all cultures
have been utterly deluded?

00:21:14.840 --> 00:21:17.150 align:middle line:10%
According to many
human conditions,

00:21:17.150 --> 00:21:21.110 align:middle line:10%
living beings can be
organized into a hierarchy.

00:21:21.110 --> 00:21:23.470 align:middle line:10%
Here a medieval
Christian picture

00:21:23.470 --> 00:21:26.420 align:middle line:10%
shows the sensory
world at the bottom,

00:21:26.420 --> 00:21:30.080 align:middle line:10%
then the celestial and
intellectual realms inhabited

00:21:30.080 --> 00:21:33.320 align:middle line:10%
by various kinds of
angels, and finally,

00:21:33.320 --> 00:21:36.590 align:middle line:10%
the eternal spiritual
domain of God.

00:21:36.590 --> 00:21:40.310 align:middle line:84%
The same idea of a progression
of ever more subtle inhabited

00:21:40.310 --> 00:21:44.180 align:middle line:84%
realms is also a part
of eastern thought.

00:21:44.180 --> 00:21:47.360 align:middle line:84%
In the esoteric teachings
of the Jewish cabala,

00:21:47.360 --> 00:21:50.000 align:middle line:84%
we find a similar
idea of a hierarchy

00:21:50.000 --> 00:21:52.700 align:middle line:90%
of emanations from God.

00:21:52.700 --> 00:21:55.280 align:middle line:84%
On the lowest levels
of such hierarchies

00:21:55.280 --> 00:21:59.110 align:middle line:84%
are power in the realms of
ghosts and earthbound spirits.

00:21:59.110 --> 00:22:01.610 align:middle line:10%
Many psychic phenomena
are attributed

00:22:01.610 --> 00:22:04.840 align:middle line:10%
to beings of this sort.

00:22:04.840 --> 00:22:06.830 align:middle line:84%
Above the ghostly
spirits, there are

00:22:06.830 --> 00:22:11.540 align:middle line:84%
found various kinds of more
powerful intermediate beings.

00:22:11.540 --> 00:22:14.000 align:middle line:84%
Beyond these are
found the demi gods,

00:22:14.000 --> 00:22:17.180 align:middle line:84%
who have control over
the forces of nature.

00:22:17.180 --> 00:22:19.850 align:middle line:84%
Also found here
are great souls who

00:22:19.850 --> 00:22:23.450 align:middle line:84%
work for the enlightenment
of all living beings.

00:22:23.450 --> 00:22:25.730 align:middle line:84%
Why have people
accepted the existence

00:22:25.730 --> 00:22:29.840 align:middle line:84%
of beings in this hierarchy,
such as demi gods?

00:22:29.840 --> 00:22:32.240 align:middle line:10%
One primary reason
is that people

00:22:32.240 --> 00:22:36.230 align:middle line:10%
have achieved definite results
by worshipping such beings.

00:22:36.230 --> 00:22:38.930 align:middle line:84%
For example, at
Lourdes in France,

00:22:38.930 --> 00:22:40.940 align:middle line:84%
physicians have
reported hundreds

00:22:40.940 --> 00:22:44.990 align:middle line:84%
of miraculous cures of
diseased and deformed people

00:22:44.990 --> 00:22:47.930 align:middle line:84%
who have bathed in the waters
of the spring connected

00:22:47.930 --> 00:22:50.660 align:middle line:84%
with an appearance
of the Virgin Mary.

00:22:50.660 --> 00:22:53.390 align:middle line:84%
Francois [INAUDIBLE],,
a French carpenter,

00:22:53.390 --> 00:22:57.560 align:middle line:84%
had an extreme case of
varicose veins for 30 years

00:22:57.560 --> 00:23:01.160 align:middle line:84%
and was declared incurable
by three physicians.

00:23:01.160 --> 00:23:04.850 align:middle line:84%
One evening, he applied
compresses with Lourdes water

00:23:04.850 --> 00:23:06.470 align:middle line:90%
to his legs.

00:23:06.470 --> 00:23:09.440 align:middle line:84%
When he awoke the next
morning, he found hardly

00:23:09.440 --> 00:23:12.380 align:middle line:90%
a trace of the varicose veins.

00:23:12.380 --> 00:23:16.280 align:middle line:84%
In such cases, the
restoration of damaged tissues

00:23:16.280 --> 00:23:20.240 align:middle line:84%
seems to be brought about by
an intelligent agency operating

00:23:20.240 --> 00:23:22.970 align:middle line:90%
outside known physical laws.

00:23:22.970 --> 00:23:26.590 align:middle line:84%
This is relevant to the
question of our origins.

00:23:26.590 --> 00:23:30.080 align:middle line:84%
If an agency can
restructure the human body,

00:23:30.080 --> 00:23:32.510 align:middle line:84%
it may have constructed
it in the first place

00:23:32.510 --> 00:23:35.390 align:middle line:84%
at any time in
geological history.

00:23:35.390 --> 00:23:37.520 align:middle line:84%
This may account for
the manufacturers

00:23:37.520 --> 00:23:40.490 align:middle line:84%
of our anomalous stone
tools and artifacts,

00:23:40.490 --> 00:23:42.890 align:middle line:84%
which seem to keep
popping up in timeframes

00:23:42.890 --> 00:23:46.670 align:middle line:84%
far too old for accepted
evolutionary theory.

00:23:46.670 --> 00:23:49.880 align:middle line:84%
But archeology reveals
nothing about living entities

00:23:49.880 --> 00:23:53.360 align:middle line:84%
above humans in the
universal hierarchy

00:23:53.360 --> 00:23:56.000 align:middle line:84%
and evolutionary
theory requires us

00:23:56.000 --> 00:24:00.140 align:middle line:84%
to regard the very idea
of such as an aberration

00:24:00.140 --> 00:24:01.910 align:middle line:90%
of the evolving brain.

00:24:01.910 --> 00:24:04.970 align:middle line:10%
But this view can be
sustained only by ignoring

00:24:04.970 --> 00:24:08.030 align:middle line:10%
vast areas of human experience.

00:24:08.030 --> 00:24:11.510 align:middle line:84%
These would include perceptions
of a supreme creator

00:24:11.510 --> 00:24:15.170 align:middle line:84%
at the root of the
universal hierarchy beings.

00:24:15.170 --> 00:24:18.320 align:middle line:84%
Plato presented the idea
of the supreme good,

00:24:18.320 --> 00:24:22.040 align:middle line:84%
the ultimate absolute cause
embodying within itself

00:24:22.040 --> 00:24:24.680 align:middle line:90%
eternal ideal forms.

00:24:24.680 --> 00:24:28.340 align:middle line:10%
He further postulated a
demiurge, a subordinate creator

00:24:28.340 --> 00:24:31.430 align:middle line:10%
who generates the material
domain by manifesting

00:24:31.430 --> 00:24:33.335 align:middle line:10%
copies of these eternal forms.

00:24:33.335 --> 00:24:38.240 align:middle line:90%


00:24:38.240 --> 00:24:40.880 align:middle line:84%
Turning to a completely
different culture,

00:24:40.880 --> 00:24:44.360 align:middle line:84%
we find that almost all
Australian aboriginal tribes

00:24:44.360 --> 00:24:50.210 align:middle line:84%
believe in a high god, sometimes
called [INAUDIBLE] or Bunjil.

00:24:50.210 --> 00:24:53.270 align:middle line:84%
This high god is
absolutely supreme

00:24:53.270 --> 00:24:57.170 align:middle line:84%
and alone is creator
and preserver.

00:24:57.170 --> 00:25:01.100 align:middle line:10%
The Chinese have traditionally
worshiped ancestral spirits,

00:25:01.100 --> 00:25:03.800 align:middle line:10%
as well as a
hierarchy of demi gods

00:25:03.800 --> 00:25:05.930 align:middle line:10%
such as the goddess of mercy.

00:25:05.930 --> 00:25:10.440 align:middle line:84%
The Chinese believed in a wide
variety of intermediate beings,

00:25:10.440 --> 00:25:13.790 align:middle line:90%
including the celestial dragons.

00:25:13.790 --> 00:25:17.990 align:middle line:84%
The Chinese also worshiped
Shang Ti, the supreme ruler

00:25:17.990 --> 00:25:21.260 align:middle line:84%
in heaven, whose name appears
on this tablet in the Imperial

00:25:21.260 --> 00:25:23.270 align:middle line:90%
Temple complex in Peking.

00:25:23.270 --> 00:25:27.440 align:middle line:84%
The Chinese emperor would
perform sacrifices to Shang Ti

00:25:27.440 --> 00:25:31.040 align:middle line:90%
in order to ensure good crops.

00:25:31.040 --> 00:25:35.390 align:middle line:84%
The American Indian shaman Black
Elk became a spiritual leader

00:25:35.390 --> 00:25:39.020 align:middle line:84%
after experiencing a vision
in which he was transported

00:25:39.020 --> 00:25:41.690 align:middle line:84%
into the presence of
guardian ancestors

00:25:41.690 --> 00:25:44.660 align:middle line:84%
from whom he received
instructions.

00:25:44.660 --> 00:25:47.960 align:middle line:84%
Black Elk saw all living
beings as the children

00:25:47.960 --> 00:25:51.230 align:middle line:90%
of one supreme spirit.

00:25:51.230 --> 00:25:54.050 align:middle line:84%
The spiritual tradition
of India embodied

00:25:54.050 --> 00:25:56.390 align:middle line:84%
in the books of the
Vedas is characterized

00:25:56.390 --> 00:25:59.210 align:middle line:90%
by many as polytheistic.

00:25:59.210 --> 00:26:03.260 align:middle line:84%
But in its pure form, it
is strongly monotheistic.

00:26:03.260 --> 00:26:06.340 align:middle line:84%
The supreme lord of the
universe, Jagannath,

00:26:06.340 --> 00:26:10.220 align:middle line:84%
is worshiped in this
famous temple in Puri.

00:26:10.220 --> 00:26:13.130 align:middle line:84%
Beyond this material
world, the Vedas teach,

00:26:13.130 --> 00:26:17.510 align:middle line:84%
there lies the Brahmajyoti,
the effulgence of the supreme.

00:26:17.510 --> 00:26:20.480 align:middle line:84%
And still higher, one
encounters of a variety

00:26:20.480 --> 00:26:21.645 align:middle line:90%
of spiritual planets.

00:26:21.645 --> 00:26:34.230 align:middle line:90%


00:26:34.230 --> 00:26:37.970 align:middle line:84%
These are predominated
by [INAUDIBLE],,

00:26:37.970 --> 00:26:42.080 align:middle line:84%
the abode of the supreme
personality of godhead Krishna

00:26:42.080 --> 00:26:46.350 align:middle line:90%
and his eternal consort, Radha.

00:26:46.350 --> 00:26:50.490 align:middle line:84%
In hierarchies described in the
world's spiritual traditions,

00:26:50.490 --> 00:26:52.190 align:middle line:90%
we find a common pattern.

00:26:52.190 --> 00:26:54.920 align:middle line:84%
This common pattern is
delineated in detail

00:26:54.920 --> 00:27:00.050 align:middle line:84%
within the highly developed
spiritual philosophy of India.

00:27:00.050 --> 00:27:04.070 align:middle line:84%
The Vedic scriptures, such as
"Bhagavad Gita" and "Srimad

00:27:04.070 --> 00:27:08.870 align:middle line:84%
Bhagavatam" describe the
supreme absolute personality.

00:27:08.870 --> 00:27:11.960 align:middle line:84%
He is the source of an
eternal spiritual realm,

00:27:11.960 --> 00:27:15.320 align:middle line:84%
as well as innumerable
temporary material universes

00:27:15.320 --> 00:27:19.250 align:middle line:84%
inhabited by souls who
have fallen into illusion.

00:27:19.250 --> 00:27:22.010 align:middle line:84%
Each universe is brought
into manifest form

00:27:22.010 --> 00:27:24.890 align:middle line:90%
by a demi urge lord Brahma.

00:27:24.890 --> 00:27:29.000 align:middle line:84%
Brahma generates material
bodies for the illusion's souls,

00:27:29.000 --> 00:27:32.270 align:middle line:84%
beginning with the great
sages and demi gods.

00:27:32.270 --> 00:27:36.150 align:middle line:84%
From the demi gods and sages,
the bodies of lesser beings--

00:27:36.150 --> 00:27:38.840 align:middle line:84%
including humans,
animals, and plants--

00:27:38.840 --> 00:27:42.410 align:middle line:84%
are generated by descent
with modification.

00:27:42.410 --> 00:27:45.650 align:middle line:84%
This can be called
inverse evolution.

00:27:45.650 --> 00:27:49.250 align:middle line:84%
The modification occurs
quickly in a manner reminiscent

00:27:49.250 --> 00:27:53.690 align:middle line:84%
of the rapid reconstruction of
the tissues seen at Lourdes.

00:27:53.690 --> 00:27:57.320 align:middle line:84%
In inverse evolution,
an existing subtle form

00:27:57.320 --> 00:28:01.160 align:middle line:84%
systematically manifests
a gross physical form.

00:28:01.160 --> 00:28:03.470 align:middle line:84%
This may be contrasted
with the generation

00:28:03.470 --> 00:28:06.290 align:middle line:84%
by generation accumulation
of slight bodily

00:28:06.290 --> 00:28:11.920 align:middle line:84%
changes postulated by
Darwinian evolutionists.

00:28:11.920 --> 00:28:15.700 align:middle line:84%
The question remains, when
did human beings actually

00:28:15.700 --> 00:28:18.340 align:middle line:90%
arrive on Earth?

00:28:18.340 --> 00:28:21.310 align:middle line:84%
The ancient Sumerians
and Babylonians

00:28:21.310 --> 00:28:25.080 align:middle line:84%
held that their first kings
descended to Earth from heaven

00:28:25.080 --> 00:28:29.360 align:middle line:84%
and that civilization was
given to man by the demi gods.

00:28:29.360 --> 00:28:33.410 align:middle line:84%
According to the "Bhagavad
Gita," about 120 million years

00:28:33.410 --> 00:28:36.500 align:middle line:84%
ago, Lord Krishna spoke
the Gita's message

00:28:36.500 --> 00:28:41.570 align:middle line:84%
to the sun god, Vivasvan,
in his residence on the sun.

00:28:41.570 --> 00:28:44.040 align:middle line:84%
Vivasvan then repeated
these instructions

00:28:44.040 --> 00:28:47.870 align:middle line:84%
to his son, Manu,
the father mankind.

00:28:47.870 --> 00:28:50.450 align:middle line:84%
About two million
years ago, Manu

00:28:50.450 --> 00:28:53.530 align:middle line:84%
passed the same instructions
to his son, [INAUDIBLE],,

00:28:53.530 --> 00:28:57.220 align:middle line:84%
who founded the dynasty
of earthly kings.

00:28:57.220 --> 00:28:59.350 align:middle line:84%
Beings from the sun
may have traveled

00:28:59.350 --> 00:29:03.400 align:middle line:84%
by means of a vimana, or
a Vedic space vehicle,

00:29:03.400 --> 00:29:07.090 align:middle line:84%
although they were capable of
more direct means of travel.

00:29:07.090 --> 00:29:10.260 align:middle line:84%
Such beings were the
progenitors of man

00:29:10.260 --> 00:29:13.600 align:middle line:84%
and also the engineers of
the natural environment

00:29:13.600 --> 00:29:14.710 align:middle line:90%
of the Earth.

00:29:14.710 --> 00:29:27.310 align:middle line:90%


00:29:27.310 --> 00:29:31.510 align:middle line:84%
Given this scheme, humans may
have been created many times

00:29:31.510 --> 00:29:33.780 align:middle line:90%
by such demi god progenitors.

00:29:33.780 --> 00:29:40.320 align:middle line:90%


00:29:40.320 --> 00:29:44.170 align:middle line:84%
Indeed, the archaeological
evidence we've considered

00:29:44.170 --> 00:29:48.100 align:middle line:84%
suggests that human beings
may have repeatedly populated

00:29:48.100 --> 00:29:51.490 align:middle line:84%
the Earth and manifested
typical cultural traits

00:29:51.490 --> 00:29:55.870 align:middle line:84%
over a course of tens
of millions of years.

00:29:55.870 --> 00:29:59.230 align:middle line:84%
Furthermore, the psychical
and anthropological material

00:29:59.230 --> 00:30:01.960 align:middle line:84%
we've reviewed
shows that humanity

00:30:01.960 --> 00:30:06.130 align:middle line:84%
may be part of a much larger
interplanetary system of life,

00:30:06.130 --> 00:30:09.760 align:middle line:84%
with its ultimate source in
an eternal transcendental

00:30:09.760 --> 00:30:11.680 align:middle line:90%
dimension.

00:30:11.680 --> 00:30:14.170 align:middle line:84%
This view allows
one to accommodate

00:30:14.170 --> 00:30:18.550 align:middle line:84%
the totality of archaeological
and anthropological evidence

00:30:18.550 --> 00:30:22.720 align:middle line:84%
available to science within
a systematic framework.

00:30:22.720 --> 00:30:25.570 align:middle line:84%
On the other hand,
Darwinian evolution

00:30:25.570 --> 00:30:28.630 align:middle line:84%
requires one to kick
out vast quantities

00:30:28.630 --> 00:30:31.570 align:middle line:84%
of archaeological
evidence and to dismiss

00:30:31.570 --> 00:30:36.020 align:middle line:84%
all paranormal and spiritual
phenomena as illusory.

00:30:36.020 --> 00:30:39.250 align:middle line:84%
Of course, by its very
nature, the evidence

00:30:39.250 --> 00:30:42.520 align:middle line:84%
available to science does
not give certain knowledge

00:30:42.520 --> 00:30:46.780 align:middle line:84%
about man's distant past
and ultimate origin.

00:30:46.780 --> 00:30:49.690 align:middle line:84%
So it may profit us to
consider higher dimensions

00:30:49.690 --> 00:30:53.410 align:middle line:84%
of human experience, rather
than confine ourselves

00:30:53.410 --> 00:30:56.730 align:middle line:84%
to seeking answers to
these questions in bones

00:30:56.730 --> 00:30:59.590 align:middle line:84%
and stones found in the
depths of the Earth.

